{"tid":913119,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會何啟明稱校園政治化令外地人才不敢來港發展","createTime":"2018-11-23T07:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T07:29:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77c97559b942cb8ccb4b4cde1cc2129d348c50db","tid":913119,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"工聯會立法會議員何啟明表示，近年院校畢業禮經常出現示威場面，認為校園政治化，加上排外情況，會令外來人才不敢到香港就學甚至就業，希望停止校園政治化，以免令外來人才不敢到香港發展，令香港進一步欠缺高端人才，亦不希望再有人利用校園成為宣示政治的平台。<br />\n<br />\n另一名工聯會議員郭偉強亦批評，有民主派人士到外地，不斷講述香港的壞消息，而不提及本港良好政策，嚇怕外來人才，令國際誤會香港言論自由和新聞自由，比新加坡更差。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429783-20181123.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429783-20181123.htm&d=dd8wLIf4IWT4QyqTJqm3%2BFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=cbfd7ad0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429783-20181123.htm&h=d326c22e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429783-20181123.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1287169a710b8dc308c3cba0dc2fc299c99c1839","tid":913119,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:26:10.000Z","msg":"on9仔，唔該你睇睇香港有幾多BDS先喇"},{"pid":"a1e0340c9706da3645cbe7840fe92d3b60c0d80e","tid":913119,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:28:23.000Z","msg":"校園政治化因為有大量中國來港學生"},{"pid":"cf91259344a75b04904d6afea26acbeb84340a74","tid":913119,"uid":92042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:29:22.000Z","msg":"啲NDS就黎多撚過local喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599ea051d6e763a66be69967faa44b69a037f330","tid":913119,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,